9. List how many comments are given by each user.
> db.post.aggregate([{$unwind:"$comments"},{$group:{_id:'$comments.user',count:{$sum:1}}}])
{ "_id" : "user4", "count" : 3 }
{ "_id" : "user3", "count" : 1 }
{ "_id" : "user2", "count" : 2 }
{ "_id" : "user1", "count" : 2 }

